                     <hi rend="smallCaps">GUILTY</hi>
                  </rs>. <hi rend="italic">He was further charged with having been convicted of felony at Carlisle in February</hi>, 1861, <hi rend="italic">to which he</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">PLEADED GUILTY</hi>.—<rs id="t18780806-741-punishment-60" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18780806-741-punishment-60" type="punishmentCategory" value="imprison"></interp>
